Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险  真的好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的空气真好啊
